body:
This PR adds the functions `traced_type_inner` and `make_tracer` to `OceananigansReactantExt` for `RectilinearGrid`. Currently there is a bug where calling `eltype` for RectilinearGrid with ReactantState architecture returns Float64, although it should return a TracedRFloat.

This PR is not yet successful. It can be tested by running the script [here](https://github.com/DJ4Earth/Channelanigans/blob/jlk9/rectilinear-grid-reactant-error/scripts/abernathey_channel.jl), which shows the fields in RectilinearGrid are still generally Float64 even with `traced_type_inner` and `make_tracer` being run.

@wsmoses
